          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘，转去，转去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侄儿这些要紧书籍，都不曾带来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勿消费心，才带拉里个哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水红花） 我欲待将言遮掩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎禁他恶狠狠把话儿揽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只得赴江干，也啰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑奶奶，到仔江边哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "进安唤船。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小船摇上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（艄公上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "撑船道业，各服一行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿是叫船？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到落里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到临安去会试个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓船家，只怕今日，江中风大，去不得吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，风没大，倒是兜艄顺风，去得个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勿要多拌，阿要几化铜钱？"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老实说，要一两笃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苏州人杀半价，五钱拉里，阿去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少点，勿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "作啥骂哉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这里到临安，有多少路，与你五钱银子，还不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘，转去，转去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢点慢点，勿要逗，依㕶么几化？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依我吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几化？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与你三分银子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘，我们转去，转去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢点慢点，我么郭璞格儿自，拗种，五钱勿去，摇㕶格三分。请下船来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀狗才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "格么八钱拉笃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘，侄儿是去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "路上小心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开船哉！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（潘必正、艄公、进安同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我且到望江楼上一看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈妙常上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （水红花） 霎时间云雨暗巫山，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满口儿何处诉愁烦？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "顾不得脚儿紧赶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，看望江楼上，好似观主模样。天吓，早是我先看见了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水红花） 若还她撞见，好羞惭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且在人家竹院，也啰。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈妙常下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侄儿去远，料他决不转来。咳，妙常吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从今割断藕丝肠，免系鹍鹏飞不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姑母下。陈妙常上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘郎吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君去也，我来迟，两下相思各自知，教我心呆意似痴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行不动，瘦腰肢，且将心事托舟师，见他强似寄封书。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想他去得不远，不免唤只小船儿，赶上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，船家，摇上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（艄婆上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "终日滩头坐，一日过九餐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小师父，阿是叫船？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到落里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要赶着前面那只会试船的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀去远哉，只怕赶勿着哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只要赶着了，船钱重谢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "格么要依我格笃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要多少，一总与你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "格么我要五钱银子笃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就与你五钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早晓得么，说子一两哉。请下船来。咦？㕶是女贞观里小师太哇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。快些开船。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢，格么开船哉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快些摇吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原是摇，勿拉里撑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啐！缆也不曾解，只管摇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拨㕶催昏子落，摇仔半日个船，缆也不曾解。让我解仔缆来看。嗳束来！那么"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开船哉。小师太，阿要泡壶茶㕶吃吃？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "格么唱只山歌㕶听听？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不要。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要听格。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快些开船。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "格么我唱哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "偏偏叫了只老船。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "艄婆 （吴歌） 吓吓吓喑，风打船头雨又来，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满天风雾了喑那哼把船开？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "㕶看白云阵阵吹黄叶。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴歌） 惟有江上芙蓉了喑独自开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为啥满肚皮格心事介？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （红衲袄） 奴好似江上芙蓉独自开，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只落得冷凄凄漂泊轻盈态。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今怎生分开鸾凤钗！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今闷昏昏独自担着害。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小师太，㕶看水面上，一对鸳鸯，拉笃打雄。咦，雄格飞子去，雌格拉笃赶上"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （红衲袄） 爱煞那一对鸳鸯在水上也，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "羞煞我哭啼啼今宵独自捱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扳得来吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈妙常、艄婆同下。潘必正、进安、艄公同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "艄公 （吴歌） 满天子介风雾日影子介暖，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "远波疏林月影子介寒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别时容易了喑见时难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伤心怕向篷窗也"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红衲袄） 我只为别时容易见时难，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看那碧澄澄断送行人江上晚。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日里愁脉脉离情有万千。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫不是锦堂欢缘分浅？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫不是蓝桥倒时运悭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂，前头格只，阿是会试船？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是，问俚作啥？"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有位女师太，要会㕶笃公子了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公，陈姑来哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （红衲袄） 堆积相思两岸山。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈妙常、艄婆同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快些摇上去吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （侥侥令） 忙追赶，去寻船，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见风里，正开帆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （侥侥令） 忽听人呼声声唤，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是何人且向前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙常，快些过船来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公、艄婆",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖哟，看仔细，几乎做大汤圆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （哭相思） 半日里抛伊不见，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "泪珠儿湿染红衫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "船家，把船泊在江口，暂停片时。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哉，搭㕶到后艄头去，燉茶吃。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（艄公、艄婆同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "事无端，恨无端，平地风波拆锦鸳，羞将泪眼向人看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这其间，那其间，恨我姑娘紧紧拦，狠心直送到江干。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早上听得师父唤我们出来送你，好不惊煞人也。不知何人，走漏消息？吖，一"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "定是你口儿不紧，以至如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生对谁说来？这是平地风波，痛肠难尽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才在众姑姑面前，有话难提，有情难诉，为此赶来送你。潘郎吓！我有千言"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万语，一时哪里说得尽吖！"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多感厚情，铭刻肺腑，早晨在众姑姑面前，一言不得相别，方抱痛肠。今得见"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿，如获珍宝。妙常吓！和你少叙片时，再作道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （同小桃红） 秋江一望泪潸潸，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕向那孤篷看，也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这别离中生出一种苦难言。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "血儿流把（你）（我）的香肌减，也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生隔断银河水，断送我春老啼鹃。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （下山虎） 黄昏月下，意惹情牵，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "才照的个双鸾镜，又早买别离船。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和你打迭凄凉今夜眠，喜见你的多情面。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又怕你难留恋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一似梦里相逢，教我愁怎言？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （五韵美） 意儿中，无别见，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "追欢别院，怕不想旧有姻缘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙常，我不是负心人㖸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘，你若负了我是——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（五韵美） 那其间，拼个死，口含冤，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和你双双罚愿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （五般宜） 想着你初相见，心甜意甜，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （五般宜） 想着你乍别时，山前水前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （五般宜） 我怎敢转眼负盟言？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （五般宜） 我怎敢忘却些儿灯边酒边？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （五般 宜 ） 只愁你形单影单。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （五般 宜 ） 又愁你衾寒枕寒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （同五般宜 ） 哭得我哽咽喉干，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠮾！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同五 般 宜 ） 一似西风泣断猿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴别君家，自当隐迹空门，洗心待君，君休负我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎敢负卿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴有碧玉鸾钗一枝，原是奴簪冠之物，将来赠君，以为加官之兆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢厚情。我有白玉鸳鸯扇坠一枚，原是君家所赐，今解来赠卿，以为他日双"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鸳之兆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠮾！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （忆多 娇 ） 两意坚，月正圆，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "执手叮咛苦挂牵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙常，和我同上临安去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我岂不欲与你同行，倘被人知道，反为不美。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（忆多 娇 ） 我欲共你同行难上难。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（艄公、艄婆同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （忆多娇） 早寄鸾笺，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "免使我心悬意悬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公、艄婆",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夜哉，要开船哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （尾声） 夕阳古道催行晚，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "暮雨朝云两下单。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公、艄婆",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "过船（去）（来）罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （同哭相思） 要知郎眼赤，只在望中看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（潘必正、陈妙常同哭下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老个，归来会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "艄公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扳得来吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（艄公、艄婆自两边分下。）"
        }
      ],
